label: Ideologic Organ
description: Staggering avant-folk hymns by France’s Karen Jebane aka Golem Mecanique, eliding haunting vocals with billowing hurdy-gurdy-like tones from a rare French instrument. She takes all the time she needs to cast two spellbinding durational works full of visceral, slow-burning and dissonant energy. Hand-picked for release on Stephen O’Malley’s Ideologic Organ... more
